quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful"
  1,2,"Praise be to God, the Lord of the Worlds"
  1,3,"The Merciful-to-all, the Mercy Giver"
  1,4,Master of the Day of Judgment
  1,5,"It is You we worship, and it is You we seek for help"
  1,6,Guide us to the straight path
  1,7,"The path of those whom You have blessed, with whom You are not angry and who have not gone astray"
